data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat at 155 Singleton Way! Nestled in the Stoncrest subdivision, this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-story rancher beckons you home. Boasting a cozy ambiance, its pristine interiors and well-maintained spaces promise comfort and convenience. Embrace the ease of single-level living and explore the potential of the unfinished basement. Conveniently situated near Route 9, its proximity to the local DMV and just a short 5-mile distance to nearby shopping markets ensure both accessibility and ease in daily living. Discover the allure of this serene abode that seamlessly blends comfort and accessibility in Martinsburg, WV.
